\id PHP
\h PHILIPPIANS
\toc1 Id ash d Paul Oꞌohana am ha Wui g Philippi t Am Wohochuththam
\toc2 PHILIPPIANS
\toc3 Php
\mt1 Id ash d Paul Oꞌohana am ha Wui g Philippi t Am Wohochuththam
\c 1
\m 
\v 1 T-wepnag mam am kih Philippi t am:
\p Am ant wo haꞌichu i em-oꞌohani ahni Paul g Timothy wehm. S-mahch am mach d piongaj g Jesus Christ namt pi ab i s-wohoch g haꞌichu t-ahga ab amjed k d Jiosh hemajkamga. Am ach s-ha ahgidamk g em-wanimeddam ch hegam mo am i ha wehmt mat ab wo i s-t-hoꞌigeꞌel.
\p 
\v 2 Ab o wa si s-em-hoꞌigeꞌid g t-ohg Jiosh g t-kownalig Jesus Christ wehm ch ab wo wa baꞌich i em-mahkad g i wehmtadag ch s-ap tahhadkam.
\s1 Mo id d Paul hoꞌigeꞌidahuna ha wehhejed
\p 
\v 3-4 Ab ani hoꞌigeꞌid g Jiosh ch si s-ap ni-tattam ch ni-hoꞌigeꞌidahun mani hekid i em-chechegitod.
\v 5 Am am chikpanid g Jiosh ch haꞌichukaj am i ni-wehmaj gd hu i amjed mani wa am em-ahgid g s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj g Jiosh.
\v 6 Kuni heg hekaj s-mahch mat am wo himchudahid g Jiosh ihda doꞌibiadag em-wehhejed. Am at i shonwuich em-doakag ed k wo nahto mat hekid ia ep wo jiwia g Jesus Christ jewed dahm.
\p 
\v 7 Bani wa masma hab em-elid nani pi chum hekid am i em-chegitod. Kum ahpim hab waꞌap chum hekid s-ni-chegito ch haꞌichukaj i ni-wehmt, chum hems hemu mani ia hu d lihso.
\v 8 Ab o ni-mahkch g Jesus Christ g si geꞌe pihk elidadag em-hekaj. K g Jiosh s-mahch mo id d wohokam mani em-ahgid.
\p 
\v 9 Kuni ab tahni mat hab wo em-juh mat baꞌich wo i geꞌeda g pihk em-elidadag ch haꞌichu em-mahchig ch haꞌichu em-amichudadag.
\v 10 Mt heg amjed wo s-mahchk hegai mo s-apꞌe mamt hab wo junihid ch pi am hu wo edak g pi apꞌekam ch pi wo ha chuꞌijigk mat hekid ep wo jiwia g Jesus Christ.
\v 11 Heg o hab em-wua mamt am wo e chehgidch mam am hab wua g s-apꞌekam haꞌichu ch heg hekaj ab haꞌichuchud g Jiosh ch ab hehgchulid.
\s1 Mattsh d wo dodakamk am wehhejed g t-doꞌibiakam
\p 
\v 12 S-em-ahgidamk ani mo baꞌich i e gantan ihda s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj g Jiosh heg hekaj mani ia kuhpi.
\v 13 Wehsijj o s-mahch ia geꞌe kownal kih am ch an wehgaj mani d lihso heg waꞌi hekaj mani d piongaj g Jesus Christ.
\v 14 K g t-wehm wohochuddam pi haꞌichu shaꞌi ehbid ch baꞌich i s-gewkam ia ahg g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga neidch mani wabsh s-ap ab nakog g ni-shoꞌigdag.
\p 
\v 15-17 Haꞌi o am hi chikpan ab si hejel e-tatchui amjed mat baꞌich wo i chum wahmud g haꞌichu pi ni-apꞌedag hemuch mani wa hu d lihso no pi s-ni-hehgamk ch wabsh ni-pipꞌichud. K wabshaba haꞌi ni-hekaj si pihk e elid ch ahgachug g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga no pi s-mahch mat g Jiosh am i ni-kei mant wo wohokamch g haꞌichu ahgaj.
\v 18 K pi has chuꞌig. Ni wabsh s-ap ni-tahtk mo e ahgachug g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga, chum as haꞌi pi ap haꞌichu e-tatchui ab am wo ahgahi.
\p 
\v 19 E am hoꞌigeꞌidahun am ni-wehhejed. K g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag i ni-wehmaj. Ni heg hekaj si s-ap ni-tahtk ch s-mahch mamt wo i ni-wuhshad.
\v 20 Tatchua ani mant chum hekid wehs hab wo juh mo haschu i ni-tatchuid g Christ pi haꞌichu ehbidch, wahm hemuch. Bant masma ab wo si has elidad wehs ni-ihbdagkaj, chum anis hems wo ni-muhkid heg hekaj.
\p 
\v 21 Neh, pi o has d ahga g ni-doakag ni-wehhejed. Chum ani hi wa s-wehmjimk g Christ. K heg hekaj chum s-apꞌe mant hu wo i muh.
\v 22-23 Ntp wabshaba d wo doakamk ch baꞌich wo i chikpandad g Christ. Ni-wehhejed o hi wa baꞌich i s-apꞌe mant wo muhk k wo wehmajk g Christ.
\v 24 K wabshaba em-wehhejed hi baꞌich i s-apꞌe mant d wo doakamk.
\v 25 Ni heg hekaj s-mahch mant d wo doakamk ch hab am wo i em-wehmajk. Mt wo i geꞌehogat am e-wohochudadag ed ch hab wo si s-ap e tahtkkad.
\v 26 Am ant wo em-wehmajk. Kumt baꞌich ab wo i si has elidad g Christ ni-hekaj.
\p 
\v 27 Bamt masma wo himad g e-doakag mamt wo haꞌichuch g s-kehg haꞌichu ahga ab amjed g Christ. Nt haha wo kah mam am e hemakochudch ch s-ap ahgachug mat g hemajkam ab wo s-wohoch g s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj g Jiosh, chum anis hems pi am hu ep wo em-nei.
\v 28 Pi g wo shaꞌi ha ehbidad hegam mo ab em-wui gegok. T heg amjed wo s-mahchk mat ab wo bei g s-koꞌok e-namkidadag. Mt ahpim ab wo bei g e-doꞌibiadag ab amjed g Jiosh.
\v 29 Do Jiosh hab elida mamt pi ab wabsh wo s-wohochudad g Christ ch wabshaba am wehhejed ep wo e shoꞌigchudad.
\v 30 Ab amt wui wo gegokkad g pi apꞌekam hab masma mam am wa neid mani hab ni-wua ch hemu kah mani hab wabsh kia ni-wua.
\c 2
\s1 Mash pi chum si e haschud g Jiosh alidag
\p 
\v 1 Bani em-elid mam s-ap ab e dagitokch Jesus Christ wui. K heg ab si i em-gewkemhun. Kum si s-ap e tahtk no pi si em-tatchua. Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am em-wehmaj. Kum aꞌai e hekaj si pihk e elid.
\v 2 Nt heg hekaj ab wo si i em-gewkemhu mamt wo i hemakoj g e-chegitoidag k ab baꞌich wo i e tatchuad ch baꞌich wo i s-ap e tahtkkad ab aꞌai e wui. Nt heg amjed wo si s-ap ni-taht.
\v 3 Pi amt wo s-chu daꞌad ch pi wo chum ge e haꞌichuchudad. Ab amt wabsh wo i e shoꞌigchudch ab aꞌai e wui ch pi waꞌi si hejel am wo e chegitod.
\v 4 Am g wo waꞌi chegitod g ha-apꞌedag haꞌi ehp, pi heg waꞌi hejel e-apꞌedag.
\p 
\v 5 Bamt masma haꞌichu wo chum chegitok mash wa g Jesus Christ ch pi hejel wo chum si e haꞌichuch.
\q1 
\v 6 Jesus Christ o d Jiosh ch wabshaba pi hab e elid mat hejel wo e wepogi g e-ohg Jiosh.
\q1 
\v 7 Ga at hu hab wabsh shaꞌi juh g e-apꞌedag k wabsh e pionchud k ia mahsi k wepo mahs mo g oꞌodham.
\q1 
\v 8 Ab o s-wohog elid g e-ohg Jiosh ch ia e shoꞌigchudahim ch ab muh kots t ab heg wa wepo masma mo d wabsh pi ap hemajkam.
\q1 
\v 9 T g Jiosh ab i wamgid k am baꞌich i si uhgkaj dahm kahchim ch ed k ab mah g gewkdag wehs haꞌichu dahm.
\q1 
\v 10 T heg hekaj wehsijj ab wo si has i elid k ab wui wo i shul hegam mo an dahm kahchim ch ed ch hegam mo an jewed dahm ch hegam mo am jewed wecho
\q1 
\v 11 k am wo ah mo ihda Jesus Christ wehs d ha-kownalig.
\q1 Neh, batt masma ab wo si has elidad g Jiosh.
\s1 Mattsh am wo i ha tashogi g hemajkam g doꞌibiadag
\p 
\v 12 Ni-naipijju, chum am hekid s-wohog elid hegai Jiosh haꞌichu ahga mani wa am em-ahgid mani eda em-wehmaj. K baꞌich d i si haꞌichu mamt ab wo s-wohog elidad hemu mani wa chum pi am hu em-wehmaj. Am g wabsh wo chikpanad ch wo geꞌegeꞌelhid am e-doꞌibiadag ed ch ab wo si has elidad g Jiosh.
\v 13 Chum o hekid em-makiog g Jiosh g tatchuidag ch gewkdag mamt am hab wo junihid g hab elidaj.
\v 14 Kumt heg am hab wo junihid pi has ahgch mamt hekid heg hekaj wo e shoꞌigch.
\v 15 T hab pi wo em-chuꞌijigch g Jiosh. Dam Jiosh aꞌaliga ch d wo chum si hekia s-apꞌekamk am ha shahgid hegam mo pi mahch g Jiosh. Idam o s-chu iꞌattomk ch totontodag. Kumt hab wo sha masmak am ha wehhejed mo g huhuꞌu am ha wehhejed g s-chuhugam k ed oiopodam
\v 16 am ha ahgidch mo g Jiosh ab ha makiog g wechij doakag. T g Jesus Christ ab wo si em-haꞌichuch mat hekid ia ep wo jiwia jewed dahm. Nt heg hekaj wo si s-hehgigk mat g ni-chikpan pi wabsh wo e nahnkogi.
\v 17 Ab amt i s-wohoch g haꞌichu ni-ahga k am i e dagito Jiosh wui hab sha masma mo wa ab wui haꞌichu e iagchulid. Kunt hemho wa wo si s-ap ni-taht mamt am wui i e dagito, chum anis hems wo ni-muhkid nani pi ahgachug g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga. Id at heg wo wa wepok mat g ni-ehꞌed wo e iawua em-wehhejed hab sha masma mo wa g nawait e iawua ab ab g iagchulida.
\v 18 Pegih, ahpim g ep wo si s-ap e tahtk ni-wehm matp g Jiosh hab wa masma wo haꞌichuch g ni-chikpan.
\s1 Matsh am wo jiwia g Timothy ha wui
\p 
\v 19 Hemu ant wo cheha g Timothy mat am wo i em-chehgim matp d wo t-kownalig Jesus tatchuik. T heg ia wo uꞌapa g haꞌichu ahga ab em-amjed mat am wo i ni-gewkemhu.
\v 20 Timothy o d waꞌi hegai mo hab wa masma hab e tahtk ab em-amjed mani ahni ch si s-ap wo em-nuhkud.
\v 21 Haꞌi o hi g hejel e-tatchui am hab elid ch wabsh pi ab hu haꞌichuchud g hab elidaj g Jesus Christ.
\v 22 Kum eda am wa s-mahch mo hab masma ni-wehm chikpan g Timothy mo g ha-alidag.
\v 23 Hemu ant wo s-mai matp haschu has wo i mahsk am ni-wehhejed. T am haha wo hih g Timothy em-wui.
\p 
\v 24 Bani elid mo d tatchuij g t-kownalig Jesus mant ahni am hab waꞌap wo i him k wo em-nei.
\s1 Matsh am uhpam wo hih g Epaphroditus ha wui
\p 
\v 25 Ia ant wo cheha g em-kehsha Epaphroditus mat am uhpam ep wo hih em-wui. Ia o i ni-wehmaj hab masma mamsh am ahgid ch muꞌi haꞌichu ni-wehm nakog.
\v 26 Msh wabshaba kah mat wa mumku. K si s-em-neidamk ch e kudut mamsh id kah.
\v 27 Woho o wa mat si mumku k chum alo muh. T wabshaba g Jiosh ab si i s-hoꞌigeꞌid k doaj. K hab waꞌap d ni-hoꞌigeꞌidadag mat pi muh nant pi wo si pi ap ni-taht mat hems wo sha muh.
\v 28 Ni heg hekaj chehani mat am uhpam wo hih. Mt hab wo si s-hehgigk am neidok. Nt ahni hab waꞌap wo si s-hehgigk ch pi wo ni-kudu em-hekaj.
\v 29-30 Kumt ab wo si has el nat pi pi huwi g e-doakag mat hab wo juh g Christ tatchui k wo i ni-wehmt em-wehhejed.
\c 3
\s1 Mamtsh has masma wo s-apꞌek am Jiosh tahgio
\p 
\v 1 Mt wabsh wo si s-hehgigk mo d em-kownalig g Jesus Christ. Pi ani has shaꞌi ni-tahtk mant am ep em-oꞌohani hegai mant wa heki hu em-oꞌohani. Kut id d wo i em-wehmtadagk.
\p 
\v 2 Haꞌi o hab junihim g pi apꞌekam ch eda chum ahgahim mamt hab wo junihid g chehanig ch hab wo i e apꞌech am Jiosh tahgio. Mt wo si s-e nenꞌoidk ab ha amjed. Bo masma pi haꞌichu amichud mo g gogogs.
\v 3 Pi am tatchua mamt wo e pahl hikuch hab masma mo heki hu chehanis matt ahchim Tutuligo hab wo t-juh. Jiosh at heki hu i em-apꞌech e wehhejed namt pi ab i s-wohoch g haꞌichu ahgaj k ab i hiw g Jesus Christ. K id heg wa wepo mam pahl hikuchkas. Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o ab t-mahkch g gewkdag ahchim mach ab s-wohochud g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga. Kuch hekaj ab si ihm g Jiosh ch ab si has elid g Jesus Christ ch pi ab hu shaꞌi hejel t-hiwig machs am oidk hab wo t-juh g chehanig k hekaj wo t-doꞌibia.
\v 4 Ahni ant baꞌich wo i ni-nako mo hegam mant ab wo hiwgad g chehanig
\v 5 nani pi d Tuhligo ch ni-pahl hikuch mani eda d gigiꞌik tash hab masma mo an oꞌohanas chehanig ch ed. Benjaminbad o d ni-shohshon ch d hema hegam gamai gohk t-shohshon ahchim Tutuligo. Dani wa Palasi mo hegam hab e elid mo pi ha chuꞌijig ab amjed g t-chehanig.
\v 6 Ha anid shoꞌigchud hegam mo ab ihm g Jesus Christ nani pi hab ha elid mo ab wui gegok g t-chehanig. Neh, banid wa masma hab ni-wua ch hekaj hab ni-elid mani pi ha chuꞌijig.
\p 
\v 7 T wabshaba am hahawa i e tashogi g Jesus Christ ni-wui. Kuni hemuch hahawa pi ab hu haꞌichuchud wehs ihda nani pi g Jesus Christ ab si haꞌichuchud.
\v 8 Wehs haꞌichu o d wabsh pi haꞌichu hahawa no pi baꞌich i s-apꞌe mant wo s-mahchk g t-kownalig Jesus Christ. Wehs ant haꞌichu s-ohhod mant wo s-mai g Jesus Christ
\v 9 k am wo i ni-hemakoj heg wehm. Heki anid hu g chehanig oidch hab ni-elid mani s-apꞌe am Jiosh tahgio. T wabshaba am hahawa i ni-tashogi g wohokam g Jesus Christ. Kunt ab i s-wohoch. T hekaj am i ni-apꞌech g Jiosh e tahgio.
\v 10 Ni hahawa tatchua mant wo si s-mahchk g Jesus Christ ch ab wo taht hegai gewkdaj mat hekaj i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed, chum anis hems hab waꞌap wo ni-shoꞌigch.
\v 11 Neh, bant wa masma hab waꞌap wo i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed mat d wo si oidchkam tashk.
\s1 Mach haschu wui chum t-nakog
\p 
\v 12 Pi ani hab kaij manis heki hu wehs ab i neid ihda ch wehs apꞌechudas ch wabshaba am ni-nakog mant heg ab wo bei mo haschu ab ni-makiog g Jesus Christ ch hekaj an ni-bei.
\v 13 Heg ant hekaj pi wo chegito mat haschu heki hu has i e juh am ni-tahgio k am wui wo ni-gewkai hegai mo haschu am ni-baꞌich.
\v 14 Neh, mo g s-melidkam am e gewkadch mat wo ha gehg k wo bei g s-ap e-namkidadag. Kuni ahni am hab waꞌap ni-gewkadch mant wo bei g s-ap ni-namkidadag. K d ihda mant an haha wo wehmajk g Christ an Jiosh kihdag ed.
\p 
\v 15 Wehsijj att hab wo wa chum t-junihid ahchim mach s-gegokim hihim g t-wohochudadag. Haꞌijj amtp hems pi hab masma hab e junihim. T wabshaba g Jiosh wo mahsko em-wuij mam haschu i pi ap hab wua.
\v 16 Am amt wo oidad g wohokam mam ab heꞌes i heki hu s-mahch ch am hab junihim.
\p 
\v 17 Am ani si s-gewkam oid g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ch am em-chehgid mamt has wo masmak. Mt wo si ha nenashanad hegam mo am hab e wua mani has i masma em-chehgid ch am ha oidk hab wo e junihid.
\v 18 Ab at e muhkid g Jesus Christ kots t ab mat wo t-doꞌibia. K eda muꞌijj ab wui gegok ihda s-kehg haꞌichu ahga. Id o si pi ap ni-tahtchud. Kuni wa muꞌikko am em-ahgid ihda heki hu ch hemu am ep em-ahgid.
\v 19 Idam o heg waꞌi ab si has elid hejel e-tatchui ch heg waꞌi s-hohhoꞌid jewed t ab haꞌichu. T g Jiosh gam hu wo i ha shul Jiawul kih ed no pi e hahaschud heg hekaj mat hekaj wo chum si e ehꞌelidad.
\v 20 Kuch wabshaba ahchim am chegito g dahm kahchim ch ed t-kihdag. Ab at amjed wo jiwia g t-doꞌibiakam Jesus Christ. Kuch ab nenida.
\v 21 Heg at gawul wo juh g mukialig t-hon heg hekaj si geꞌe e-gewkdag mat hekaj wehs haꞌichu wo dahmkad. T g t-hon si s-kehg hab wo masmak hab masma mo g honaj si s-kehg hab mahs ab i wuhshanik muhkig amjed.
\c 4
\s1 Mo g Paul am haꞌichukaj i ha shelinid
\p 
\v 1 Pegih, ab amt i s-wohoch g haꞌichu ni-ahga ab amjed g t-kownalig Jesus. M d hahawa si ni-tatchuidch ni-wepnag. Ni heg hekaj si s-ap ni-tahtk ch chum si s-em-neidamk. S-gegokim g wo gegokkad am eda g e-wohochudadag.
\p 
\v 2 Ab ani s-em-ahgidamk ahpim Euodia ch Syntyche mamt pi wo e neꞌowinad ch am wabsh wo i e wehmajk nam pi d e wehm wohochuddam.
\v 3 Idam uꞌuwi o am si i ni-wehmajkahim mach wa am ahgachug g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga. Ni heg hekaj am ep s-m-ahgidamk ahpi map hab e chechcheg I-ha-Wehmtdam mapt woho am wo i ha wehmajk map hab masma i ni-wehmajkahim. Clement ch haꞌi ehp o hab waꞌap i ni-wehmajkahim. Pi o wehs s-e mahch g ha-chechgig ch wabshaba an oꞌohadag heg eda mo an e oꞌohan g e doꞌibiakam ha-chechgig ch an kahch Jiosh kihdag ed.
\p 
\v 4 Si g wo s-hehgig ab amjed g t-kownalig Jesus Christ mani hab masma chum hekid hab chechꞌe.
\v 5 E o aihim mat ep wo jiwia. Kumt heg hekaj wabsh wo i s-hehemajimak ab wehs ha wui g hemajkam.
\v 6 Pi g wo shaꞌi e kudut heg hekaj mam haschu i chum tatchua k ab wabsh wo i tai g Jiosh k ab wo i hoꞌigeꞌel matp haschu hab wo i t-juni.
\v 7 T g Jiosh ab wo em-mahkad g s-ap tahhadkam. K ihda s-ap tahhadkam pi ta amichudama ch wabshaba wo chehmo g t-dodakag. Kutt hab pi haꞌichukaj wo t-kudutad ahchim matt ab i t-hemakoch g Jesus Christ wehm.
\p 
\v 8 Am g wo chegitok wehs ihda mo haschu d s-apꞌekam k ab wo hehgchulidad g Jiosh heg amjed mo haschu d wohokam ch haschu d si oꞌodhamdag ch haschu d s-apꞌekam ch haschu s-kehgaj.
\v 9 Am g wo i e mashcham k hab wo junihid hegai mam haschu i kahk ch ab bei ni-amjed. Kut wo e chehgi mo am em-wehmaj hegai mat t-doꞌibia k ab t-mahkch g s-ap tahhadkam.
\s1 Mash wa g Paul si s-ap e tahtk mamt ab haꞌichu mah
\p 
\v 10 Si geꞌe s-hehgig ant bei ab amjed g Jiosh mamt ab ep i e chehgi mam ab si pihk e elid ni-wui. Tash o pi am hu em-apꞌe mams ab haꞌichu wo ni-mah k wo i ni-wehmt. Ni wabshaba s-mahch mam si pihk e elid ni-hekaj.
\v 11 Ni pi hab ahgch hab kaij manis haꞌichu si tatchua nant pi s-mai mant ab wabsh wo si s-ap ni-tahtkk mani haschu i edgid,
\v 12 chum anis hebaichujj wo bihugim k pi haꞌichu wo edgidad o hebaichujj geꞌe haꞌichu wo edgidad.
\v 13 Jesus Christ o ab ni-mahkch g gewkdag. Nt heg hekaj wo ni-nako mant s-ap am hab wo junihid g Jiosh tatchui.
\p 
\v 14 K wabshaba si s-apꞌe mamt am i ni-wehmt pi ni-apꞌedag ed.
\v 15 S-mahch am ahpim Philippi t am wohochuddam mam d waꞌi ahpim ch am i ni-wehmaj am i dahm mant am em-dagito am uꞌapak g s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj g Jiosh amai Macedonia jewed ch ed.
\v 16 Ni hebaichujj haꞌichu tatchua ab Thessalonica kihhim t ab. Kum ab ni-mamka.
\v 17 Pi o hab mahs manis heg ab waꞌi tatchua em-mahkig. Baꞌich ani i tatchua mamt ab wo bei g hoꞌigeꞌidalig ab amjed g Jiosh.
\v 18 Ia at uꞌapa g em-mahkig g Epaphroditus. Kuni hahawa pi haꞌichu shaꞌi tatchua. Em-mahkig o hab sha masma mo hegai s-ap uhw haꞌichu mo wa ab e iagchulid Jiosh wui. K g Jiosh ab si s-hohhoꞌid
\v 19 ch hab waꞌap wo em-mahkad mam haschu i tatchua. Ab o e chehgidch ab amjed g Jesus Christ mo g Jiosh geꞌe haꞌichu an toꞌakch am t-wehhejed.
\v 20 Chum att hekid wo hehgchulidad g Jiosh t-ohg! Chum hekid!
\s1 Mash am haꞌi ep s-ha hoꞌigeꞌid
\p 
\v 21 Ab amt wo ha ahgi g t-wehm wohochuddam mat ab wo i s-ni-hoꞌigeꞌel. Ni-wehm chikpandam iia o hab waꞌap kaij mamt ab wo i s-ha hoꞌigeꞌel.
\v 22 K wehsijj g t-wehm wohochuddam hab waꞌap kaij, wahm hegam mo ia haꞌichug geꞌe kownal kih ed.
\p 
\v 23 Neh, ab at wo wa baꞌich i s-em-hoꞌigeꞌidad g t-kownalig Jesus Christ.
